com.ryanantkowiak.jOptionsHouseAPI
Class OhOrderDetails

java.lang.Object
  com.ryanantkowiak.jOptionsHouseAPI.IOh
      com.ryanantkowiak.jOptionsHouseAPI.OhOrderDetails

public class OhOrderDetails
extends IOh

This class will retrieve the details about one order at OptionsHouse. Order details are grouped into "Legs", with each leg containing data such as the security key, the quantity, fill quantity, etc. One order can have multiple legs. For example, a buy-write covered call order has two legs One leg is holding the shares of the underlying stock. The other leg is the short position on the call option that was written/sold.

Author:
Ryan Antkowiak
